<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,1197,1222]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Distribution.</emphasis>
Only known from 
<collectingCountry box="[567,635,1197,1222]" name="Brazil" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(Roraima).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
